治性考量的情況下，請以經濟學理和實務的觀點評論之。（請至少提出
兩個觀點）（10分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:21:38+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "49f91d94d33d", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114140", "c": "104", "s": "1105", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "國際經濟", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年公務人員特種考試外交領事人員及外交行政人員考試、國際經濟商務人員考試、民航人員考試、原住民族考試", "original_question_number": "一", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "diplomatic", "civil_category": "外交領事人員-法文組"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('diplomatic-ea72210e-moex-00035', 'diplomatic-ea72210e', 'diplomatic-ea72210e-moex-114-e6f33b51', 'sub-diplomatic-ea72210e-03', NULL, 'essay', '區域貿易協定在世界貿易組織（World Trade Organization,WTO）杜哈
